text: The Patchwork Girl of Oz is a 1914 American fantasy adventure movie directed by J. Farrell MacDonald and was based on the 1913 novel of the same name by L. Frank Baum. It stars Violet MacMillan, Frank Moore, Raymond Russell, Hal Roach, Fred Woodward, Bert Glennon and was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1914 movies Category:1910s fantasy movies Category:1910s adventure movies Category:American fantasy movies Category:American adventure movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by J. Farrell MacDonald Category:Paramount Pictures movies
